                "Text": "<h2 style=\"margin-left:0px;\">A Note From: Katharine Bailey</h2><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">Hi everyone,</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">First and foremost, congratulations to everyone whose work SHINED during our recent Look Back / Look Forward presentations. There have been some massive wins this past H2, and I’m very impressed with the KRs and initiatives targeted for H1 this year.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://forms.gle/4keRFnZdYSHT4tPf7\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong><u>Please tell us what you thought by filling out this survey</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">! Your feedback is invaluable for making these sessions more effective and beneficial in the future.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">Please find all recordings below:</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Day 1:</strong></span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rpZNnjpsBeUsWGfahZfrvBQBPMHzBZMZ/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Introduction</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hfjluddn4kZEGJY1Ng-MZNtRG3cAC3RO/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Project Management &amp; Team Health</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ANhqIxttkXExld7jvcovCo_pH0N_sS8F/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Technology Engagement &amp; Marketing</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HZlJbCyxX760slE33SixYx882xIxU1Nz/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>People &amp; Learning Development Team</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pMbBesiS1d01iei8JO_sTo38K-ERWM8Y/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Enterprise Technology —&nbsp;Enterprise Platforms &amp; Global Support</u></span></a></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Day 2:</strong></span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1giG1Z536ojaMPkQlYo9h3rn6373za3vs/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Cyber Security</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FYHmZqT4zwzsuyfeWb7QZw_2K_EOTopS/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Digital Communications</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vvE8mJL7bTivx8kl6adjMqdxdUWC-pbO/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Infrastructure</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mRwCXdxOKe2fErR2InR-8NnlAxrB_KVg/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Data Catalog, Data Quality, KPI Governance, Consent &amp; Compliance</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bNVcBu7m8ReRgXSTruXnCgEFdWWXBoNG/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Customer Data &amp; Orchestration pt. 1</u></span></a></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Day 3:</strong></span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EBneUdsDmun0DLCCEu-4LSFhJpmWJpxb/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Customer Data pt. 2</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Z_vFS8USMKwH5o7Egco1lB0sHV9npi0R/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Revenue Intro and Subscriptions &amp; Memberships</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nUpcxgfJnKKUcEbybz8rUcadAGyuk2zN/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Commerce</u></span></a></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Day 4:</strong></span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1of8MYgdz0ho7l2_NNELNWbwglZ_fdauT/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Publishing Platform</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1YMh-P-W-t5dFhRa7SKfC1CUx1OYUUCIo/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Engagement</u></span></a></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong>Day 5:</strong></span></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UZcLjixH2A1YRYFwYBpIHVNRO-uG5tFq/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Commercial</u></span></a></li><li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EVCzfQ6E3xG4klqBDZh5MNMEaW3xeS1r/view?usp=drive_link\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);\"><u>Content &amp; Engagement Dashboards&nbsp;</u></span></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1-kxRQDulUnYw8pkYhoLeb8VhOu-DLAsi9USFxBdU8OY/edit#slide=id.g25596a48485_0_376\"><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><strong><u>The master deck with all presentations can be found here</u></strong></span></a><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\"><u>.</u></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">Thanks again to all of our fantastic presenters so far for bringing our OKRs and work to life.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);color:hsl(0, 0%, 100%);font-family:&quot;Libre Franklin&quot;, sans-serif;\">Katharine</span></p>",
